Package com.buffettinc.hrms.model.pto

Class PTORequest

java.lang.Object
com.buffettinc.hrms.model.pto.PTORequest
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
@Entity public class PTORequest extends Object implements Serializable
This class represents a PTORequest to be used by Employee of Buffett Inc. Each PTORequest consists of a reference to the employee with their employeeID, the start date of the request, end date, a reason, a status, and a reference to the approver.
